node.text: Find out where you livin’. ✨Pistachio magic with @emcdowell.
But also like, the right to choose.
You got options, but I been chosen. 🙏

You took me places, you spent that
They said no, we went back
Checks bounced but we bounced back
I put all the money in your accounts back ✨💓 Tell your mama this weekend!
Damn, where my roof just go?
